我使用vue-cli来初始化一个Demo,用的模板是webpack-simple。其目的是编写一个loading插件，可是编写完后，出现Failed to mount component: template or render function not defined.的错误。

环境描述:
`"vue": "^2.4.4"`

Loading.vue:
`<template>
    <div class="loading-container">
        <span class="three-quarters-loader"></span>
    </div>
</template>
<style scoped>
    @-moz-keyframes three-quarters-loader {
        0% {
            -moz-transform: rotate(0deg);
            transform: rotate(0deg);
        }
        100% {
            -moz-transform: rotate(360deg);
            transform: rotate(360deg);
        }
    }
    @-webkit-keyframes three-quarters-loader {
        0% {
            -webkit-transform: rotate(0deg);
            transform: rotate(0deg);
        }
        100% {
            -webkit-transform: rotate(360deg);
            transform: rotate(360deg);
        }
    }
    @keyframes three-quarters-loader {
        0% {
            -moz-transform: rotate(0deg);
            -ms-transform: rotate(0deg);
            -webkit-transform: rotate(0deg);
            transform: rotate(0deg);
        }
        100% {
            -moz-transform: rotate(360deg);
            -ms-transform: rotate(360deg);
            -webkit-transform: rotate(360deg);
            transform: rotate(360deg);
        }
    }
    /* :not(:required) hides this rule from IE9 and below */
    .three-quarters-loader:not(:required) {
        -moz-animation: three-quarters-loader 1250ms infinite linear;
        -webkit-animation: three-quarters-loader 1250ms infinite linear;
        animation: three-quarters-loader 1250ms infinite linear;
        border: 4px solid #20A4FF;
        border-right-color: transparent;
        border-radius: 23px;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        overflow: hidden;
        text-indent: -9999px;
        width: 46px;
        height: 46px;
        display: block;
        margin: -23px;
        position: absolute;
        left: 50%;
        top: 50%;
    }
    .loading-container{
        width: 100px;
        height: 100px;
        position: fixed;
        left: 50%;
        top: 50%;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        -webkit-transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        -ms-transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        -moz-transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        z-index: 222;
        text-align: center;
    }
</style>`


loading.js:

`const LoadingComponent = require("./Loading.vue");
const loading = {
    install: function(Vue) {
        //挂载组件
        Vue.component('loading', LoadingComponent)
    }
};

module.exports = loading`

然后我在main.js中引入:
`import loading from './lib/loading'
Vue.use(loading);`

并在App.vue中使用这个loading插件报Failed to mount component: template or render function not defined错误

